                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">Professional Dental Implant Surgery in Nairobi</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 text-lg">Surgical implant placement is the stage where a titanium implant is carefully inserted into the jawbone to act as an artificial tooth root.</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8">The implant creates a stable base for a crown, bridge, or other replacement tooth. Over time, it integrates with the bone through osseointegration, helping restore long-term strength and function.</p>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="flex items-start">
