                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">Who Needs Dental Implants?</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">Dental implants may be recommended for patients who have lost one or more teeth due to decay, injury, gum disease, or long-term tooth damage.</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
                        <li class="flex items-start"><i class="fas fa-check text-accent mr-3 mt-1"></i>Missing one tooth or several teeth</li>
