                        <li class="flex items-start"><i class="fas fa-check text-accent mr-3 mt-1"></i>Wanting stable support for a crown or bridge</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start"><i class="fas fa-check text-accent mr-3 mt-1"></i>Healthy enough for planned dental surgery</li>
                    </ul>
