                <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">Benefits of Dental Implants</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Implants improve chewing ability, restore natural appearance, and help maintain jawbone structure by reducing bone loss after tooth loss.</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">They do not rely on neighboring teeth for support, which helps preserve surrounding teeth and overall dental health.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
